## Task Dependency Summary

```mermaid
graph TD
    P1[Phase 1: Scaffold] --> P2[Phase 2: Auth]
    P1 --> P3[Phase 3: Shell & Sidebar]
    P2 --> P3
    P1 --> P4[Phase 4: Upload & PII]
    P3 --> P4
    P3 --> P5[Phase 5: Chat & Pipeline]
    P5 --> P6[Phase 6: Output & Charts]
    P4 --> P7[Phase 7: Polish]
    P6 --> P7
```

> [!NOTE]
> **Phase 3** depends on Phase 2 (auth context needed for sidebar user info). **Phase 5** can start as soon as Phase 3 is done (sidebar provides dataset/conversation context). **Phase 4** and **Phase 5** can be worked on in parallel by two people.
